INSERT INTO "stories" VALUES(32,'Out on the streets','One of the pure unadulterated joys of Dig It is standing (pedalling?) shoulder to shoulder with people who share the same views and values as we do...it''s why going on marches is an integral facet of the DISS, and who can deny the joys of putting smiles on faces with a politically charged set in a bit of the capital where you don''t generally get to wave your arms or shake your thing? 
INSERT INTO "stories" VALUES(33,'May Day, May Day....','Oh how I love a celebration - so much so, that I''m more than happy to hijack other peoples knees ups to get right in there and get involved...so when we were asked to help our friends at the amazing charity Global Generation do a ''Christmas'' party at the Skip Garden in King''s Cross, I stuck my ''bah humbug, Christmas ain''t one for me'' vibe away and was there with jingle-bells on...
